; SAND — Desert with central pyramid.
; Landmarks: Central Pyramid (4 stepped tiers, 4 entrances), Oasis Pools,
;   Quicksand Pit, Buried Ruin Pavilion (pillars + lintels), Obelisk.
; Tiers: desert floor / pyramid steps / pyramid apex.
; 11 enemies (goombas patrols, 2 chain chomps guarding pyramid, koopas,
;   bobombs in ruins), 30 coins, apex star, hidden ruin 1-up, metal cap.

